propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propCompleted: Mark the step as completed. Is passed to child components.
propIcon: The label displayed in the step icon.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesText: Styles applied to the SVG text element.
stylesActive: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `active={true}`.
stylesCompleted: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `completed={true}`.
stylesError: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `error={true}`.
